dc_description_s: This dataset is a polygon shapefile of the spatial extents of rectified railroad valuation map images. The image corresponding to each of the map footprints contains information about the railroad ownership, the map roll number, sheet numbers and file name of the image.
dc_creator_sm: Minnesota Department of Transportation, Office of Land Management
dc_relation_sm: Railroad coverage including abandoned lines, Railroad Station Plat images, Railroad Valuation images, Railroad Right of Way map, State basemap (active railroad lines), 1936 County Map Series with Government Lots, Sections, Townships and Ranges, other Minnesota Railroad and Warehouse Commission Historical Railroad documents.
